bibdata.title: IEEE Recommended Practice for Test Methods for Determination of Compatibility of Materials With Conductive Polymeric Insulation Shields and Jackets
IEEE Recommended Practice for Test Methods for Determination of Compatibility of Materials With Conductive Polymeric Insulation Shields and Jackets

organization.name: Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers

bibdata.abstract: In this IEEE Standard a test method is provided to qualify various essentially nonvolatile, highly viscous fluids or solid materials at 90/spl deg/C, for use with high-voltage cable shields and jackets. A suggested alternative test method for more fluid and more volatile materials is also provided.
